%% 3.1.10 Account Management (Staff) — sequence (layered)
%% Actor > UI > Controller > Service > Repository > Database

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Super Admin
    participant UI as UI (/accounts)
    participant UC as Controller (UserController)
    participant US as Service (UserService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository User Role)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    Note over Actor,DB: BR10 — route guard: only Super Admin (JWT Role claim + policy)

    Actor->>UI: Add Staff — fill form, Role Staff
    UI->>UC: POST /api/User/Create UserCreateDto
    UC->>US: CreateUserAsync
    US->>Repo: Add user + hash password + role Staff
    Repo->>DB: INSERT
    US-->>UC: UserDto
    UC-->>UI: 200

    Actor->>UI: Import — drag new_staff.csv into drop zone
    UI->>UC: POST /api/User/Import multipart form
    UC->>US: ImportAsync(dto)
    US->>US: Parse Excel rows, validate
    loop Each row
        US->>Repo: Add users
        Repo->>DB: INSERT batch
    end
    US-->>UC: UserImportResultDto
    UC-->>UI: 200 — progress complete, refresh list
